Document: backuppc
Title: BackupPC Documentation
Author: Craig Barratt
Abstract: BackupPC is a high-performance, enterprise-grade system for
 backing up Linux, Windows and macOS PCs and laptops to a server's disk.
 BackupPC is highly configurable and easy to install and maintain.
